0.1.0.name: wordpress/cf-image-gallery
0.1.0.description: Cf Image Gallery create image gallery from attachment images. write shortcode to content and upload images, only. I recomend use some plugins together, these plugins is "Custom Field Template" and "Additional Image Sizes (zui)".
